{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/react/define-an-html-class-in-jsx","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"react","demoType":null,"title":"Objasni HTML element u JSX-u","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada počnete da učite JSX, verovatno ćete se zapitati koje su mu razlike u odnosu na HTML.</p>\n<p>Do sada izgleda kao da su HTML i JSX potpuno isti.</p>\n<p>Glavna razlika u JSX-u je što više ne možete koristiti reč <code>class</code> za kreiranje klasa za HTML. Ovo je zato što <code>class</code> je rezervisana reč u JavaScript. Umesto toga, JSX koristi <code>className</code>.</p>\n<p>Zapravo, konvencija imenovanja za sve svojstva elementa HTML i reference na događaje u JSX je camelCase. Na primer, klik događaj u JSX je <code>onClick</code>, umesto <code>onclick</code>. Slično tome, <code>onchange</code> se menja u <code>onChange</code>. Iako je ovo mala razlika, važno je imati na umu kada idete dalje.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a24c314108439a4d4036160","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Primeni klasu <code>myDiv</code> na element <code>div</code> u JSX kodu.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301393,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/react/define-an-html-class-in-jsx"},"required":[{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react/16.4.0/umd/react.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom-test-utils.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom-server.browser.production.min.js"}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexjsx","ext":"jsx","name":"index","contents":"const JSX = (\n  <div>\n    <h1>Add a class to this div</h1>\n  </div>\n);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.jsx"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Element <code>JSX</code> treba da vrati element <code>div</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(JSX.type, 'div');"},{"text":"<p><code>div</code> treba da ima klasu od <code>myDiv</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(JSX.props.className, 'myDiv');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#react","dashedName":"define-an-html-class-in-jsx","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"react","isFirstStep":false,"template":"<body><div id='root'></div><div id='challenge-node'></div>${ source || '' }</body>","required":[{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react/16.4.0/umd/react.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom-test-utils.production.min.js"},{"link":null,"src":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/react-dom/16.4.0/umd/react-dom-server.browser.production.min.js"}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/react/learn-about-self-closing-jsx-tags","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/react/render-html-elements-to-the-dom","id":"5a24c314108439a4d4036160","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":6,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"jsx","contents":"class App extends React.Component {\n  constructor(props) {\n    super(props);